@startuml
title View tests assigned to a user

|User|
start
:Selects a user;

|System|
:Displays user profile;
:Evaluates application statuses in the background;
:Updates statuses in database;

note right
  Por comenzar: no tests graded
  En proceso: at least one test graded
  Completada: all tests graded
  Caducada: incomplete tests past expiry threshold

  Clinical: 3 months
  Research: 6 months
end note

|User|
:Selects an application;

|System|
:Fetches tests assigned to the application;

if (Is application expired?) then (yes)
  :Shows expiry banner;
endif

:Displays test cards with current status;

note right
  Por comenzar
  En proceso
  Calificada
  Caducada
end note

stop
@enduml